name: Desy Duk
description: The project centers around Desy Duk, a comical spin on the beloved Daisy Duck, emerging from the popular Dolanverse. Desy is here to spread laughter and joy, collaborating with other iconic characters from the Dolanverse like Dolan, Gooby, and Morky. Together, they create hilarious, meme-worthy moments that entertain and engage the community. This project focuses on delivering a steady stream of humorous, hand-drawn content that taps into the viral energy of meme culture.
